  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "柯尔特 M1911A1 .45 ACP 手枪",
      "en": "Colt M1911A1 .45 ACP pistol"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "M1911A1",
      "en": "M1911A1"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 31,810₽ | 物品价值: 5,408 | Mechanic报价: 3,028₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 14,323₽\n购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级1 < 102$ ≈ 12,296₽\n\nM1911和“柯尔特”一样人尽皆知，是世界上最著名的手枪之一。它是经历了两次世界大战的美国陆军标准制式手枪，尽管它在1986年被取代，在各种美国特种部队中，它的各种现代改进型号仍然是作为便携武器的选择之一。M1911A1 是M1911手枪的未来产品，在第一次世界大战之后，Model 1911 军用手枪经历了各种变化，包括较短的带框架切口的扳机、改进的瞄具、拱形主弹簧外壳和重新设计的安全握把。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 31,810₽ | 物品价值: 5,408 | Mechanic报价: 3,028₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 14,323₽\n购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级1 < 102$ ≈ 12,296₽\n\nCommonly known as just \"1911\", the M1911 is one of the most famous handguns on the planet. It went through both World Wars as the US Army's standard-issue, and despite being replaced in 1986, its further variations are still being used as the sidearm of different US Special Forces. The M1911A1 is the second generation of the original M1911 pistol. After World War I, the military's Model 1911 went through various changes including a shorter trigger with frame cuts, improved iron sights, an arched mainspring housing, and a redesigned grip safety."
    },
